HEADWORD: Disclaunder
<hw>Dis*claun"der</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[From OE.
<ets>disclaundre</ets>, <ets>n.</ets>, for <ets>sclandre</ets>,
<ets>esclandre</ets>, OF. <ets>esclandre</ets>. See <er>Sclaundre</er>,
<er>Slander</er>.]</ety> <def>To injure one's good name; to
